</div><div class="sect1">
<h2 id="300">3. Generating several entry certificates</h2>
<div class="sectionbody">
<div class="paragraph">
<p>If you wish to generate several entry certificates at a time, use the search filter in the <strong>Orders » Fulfilment</strong> menu to determine the orders for which entry certificates should be generated. In addition, a status change can take place after the entry certificates have been generated.</p>
</div>
<div class="paragraph instruction">
<p>Generating several entry certificates:</p>
</div>
<div class="olist arabic">
<ol class="arabic">
<li>
<p>Go to <strong>Orders » Fulfilment » Generate entry certificate (Gelangensbestätigung)</strong>.</p>
</li>
<li>
<p>Carry out the settings according to <a href="#table-settings-fulfilment-entry-certificate">Table 2</a></p>
</li>
<li>
<p>Click on the <strong>gear-wheel icon</strong> to generate the entry certificates.<br>
→ A <strong>PDF file</strong> containing the entry certificates for the previously selected orders opens.</p>
</li>
</ol>
</div>
